<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Website Disclaimer</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #000;
            padding: 60px 80px;
            background: white;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #000;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .document-title {
            font-size: 24pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 15px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .date {
            text-align: right;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: #f8f8f8;
            border: 2px solid #333;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .info-box h3 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .info-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 200px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .info-value {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .section {
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .section-content {
            text-align: justify;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        ul {
            margin-left: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .warning-box {
            background: #fff9e6;
            border: 2px solid #d4a900;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .warning-box strong {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
        <div class="document-title">WEBSITE DISCLAIMER</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Date -->
    <div class="date">Last Updated: {{date}}</div>

    <!-- Business Information Box -->
    <div class="info-box">
        <h3>Business Information</h3>

        <div class="info-row">
            <div class="info-label">Business Name:</div>
            <div class="info-value">{{BusinessName}}</div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-row">
            <div class="info-label">Website:</div>
            <div class="info-value">{{Website}}</div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-row">
            <div class="info-label">Contact Email:</div>
            <div class="info-value">{{Email}}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Warning Box -->
    <div class="warning-box">
        <strong>IMPORTANT NOTICE</strong>
        The information provided on this website is for general informational and educational purposes only. It is not
        intended to be a substitute for professional medical, legal, financial, or other expert advice.
    </div>

    <!-- Section 1 -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">1. NO PROFESSIONAL ADVICE</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            The content on <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong>'s website, including blog posts, videos, social media,
            emails, and other materials, is provided for informational and educational purposes only.
        </div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>Nothing on this website constitutes:</strong>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li>Medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment recommendations;</li>
            <li>Legal advice or representation;</li>
            <li>Financial, investment, or tax advice;</li>
            <li>Mental health counseling or therapy;</li>
            <li>Nutritional or dietary advice from a licensed dietitian; or</li>
            <li>Any other form of professional advice.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="section-content">
            You are strongly encouraged to consult with qualified professionals (physicians, attorneys, financial
            advisors, etc.) before making any decisions based on information found on this website.
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 2 -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">2. NO GUARANTEES OR WARRANTIES</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> makes no representations or warranties of any kind, express or implied,
            regarding:
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li>The accuracy, completeness, reliability, or currentness of the information on this website;</li>
            <li>The results, outcomes, or benefits you may or may not achieve from using our services, products, programs,
                or information;</li>
            <li>The fitness of our services for your particular needs or circumstances; or</li>
            <li>That the website will be error-free, uninterrupted, or free from viruses or harmful components.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>All information and services are provided "AS IS" and "AS AVAILABLE" without any warranty
                whatsoever.</strong>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 3 -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">3. HEALTH AND FITNESS DISCLAIMER</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Participation in physical activities such as yoga, pilates, fitness classes, personal training, retreats, or
            wellness programs involves inherent risks, including but not limited to the risk of injury, illness, or
            death.
        </div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>Before beginning any exercise or wellness program, you should:</strong>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li>Consult with a licensed physician, especially if you have pre-existing medical conditions, injuries, or
                are pregnant;</li>
            <li>Obtain medical clearance to participate in physical activities;</li>
            <li>Inform instructors of any health concerns, limitations, or injuries;</li>
            <li>Listen to your body and stop any activity that causes pain or discomfort.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="section-content">
            By participating in any activities offered by <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong>, you acknowledge that you do
            so at your own risk and assume full responsibility for your health and safety.
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 4 -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">4. RESULTS NOT GUARANTEED</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Testimonials, success stories, case studies, and examples of results shared on this website represent the
            experiences of specific individuals and are not guarantees of results you will achieve.
        </div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Your results may vary depending on numerous factors, including but not limited to:
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li>Your individual effort, consistency, and commitment;</li>
            <li>Your starting point, goals, and personal circumstances;</li>
            <li>Your physical condition, age, and health status;</li>
            <li>External factors beyond our control.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> does not guarantee any specific outcomes, results, weight loss, muscle gain,
            stress reduction, or other benefits from our services or programs.
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 5 -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">5. THIRD-PARTY CONTENT AND LINKS</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            This website may contain links to third-party websites, products, services, or resources. We do not endorse,
            control, or assume responsibility for any third-party content.
        </div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> is not liable for:
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li>The accuracy or reliability of third-party information;</li>
            <li>The quality, safety, or legality of third-party products or services;</li>
            <li>Any damages, losses, or issues arising from your use of third-party websites or services;</li>
            <li>The privacy practices of third-party websites (please review their privacy policies).</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="section-content">
            Your use of any third-party links is at your own risk.
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 6 -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">6. AFFILIATE DISCLOSURES</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> may earn commissions or receive compensation when you purchase products or
            services through affiliate links on this website. This does not increase your cost.
        </div>
        <div class="section-content">
            We only recommend products and services we genuinely believe provide value. However, we are not responsible
            for the quality, performance, or outcomes of any third-party products or services.
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 7 -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">7. ASSUMPTION OF RISK</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            By using this website or participating in any services offered by <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong>, you
            acknowledge and assume all risks associated with:
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li>Relying on information provided on this website;</li>
            <li>Participating in physical activities, wellness programs, or online courses;</li>
            <li>Using products, equipment, or facilities;</li>
            <li>Interacting with instructors, staff, or other participants.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="section-content">
            You expressly waive any claims against <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> for injuries, damages, or losses
            arising from your use of this website or participation in our services.
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 8 -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">8. LIMITATION OF LIABILITY</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong>, its owners, employees, instructors,
            contractors, agents, and affiliates shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential,
            special, or punitive damages arising from:
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li>Your use of (or inability to use) this website;</li>
            <li>Any errors, omissions, or inaccuracies in the content;</li>
            <li>Reliance on information provided on this website;</li>
            <li>Participation in our services, programs, or activities;</li>
            <li>Unauthorized access to your data or account;</li>
            <li>Any other matter related to this website or our services.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="section-content">
            Some jurisdictions do not allow the exclusion of certain warranties or limitations of liability, so these
            limitations may not apply to you.
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 9 -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">9. INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            All content on this website, including text, images, videos, graphics, logos, and other materials, is the
            intellectual property of <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> and is protected by copyright, trademark, and other
            laws.
        </div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>You may not:</strong>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li>Copy, reproduce, distribute, or publicly display our content without permission;</li>
            <li>Use our content for commercial purposes without a license;</li>
            <li>Modify, create derivative works, or reverse engineer our content;</li>
            <li>Use our content to train AI models, algorithms, or datasets without express written consent.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="section-content">
            Unauthorized use of our intellectual property may result in legal action.
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 10 -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">10. CHANGES TO DISCLAIMER</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> reserves the right to update, modify, or revise this Disclaimer at any time
            without prior notice. Your continued use of this website after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance
            of the updated Disclaimer.
        </div>
        <div class="section-content">
            We encourage you to review this Disclaimer periodically.
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 11 -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">11. GOVERNING LAW</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            This Disclaimer shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of
            <strong>{{Jurisdiction}}</strong>, without regard to conflict of law principles.
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 12 -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">12. CONTACT INFORMATION</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            If you have any questions about this Disclaimer, please contact us:
        </div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong><br>
            {{BusinessAddress}}<br>
            Email: {{Email}}<br>
            Phone: {{Phone}}
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Acknowledgement -->
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">ACKNOWLEDGEMENT</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            By using this website, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by this
            Disclaimer. If you do not agree with any part of this Disclaimer, please discontinue use of this website
            immediately.
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>